  <brief_title>Post Market Clinical Follow Up Study of Avance Foam Abdominal Dressing Kit in Open Abdomen</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Centre, Post CE Mark, Open Clinical Investigation to Evaluate an Abdominal NPWT (Negative Pressure Wound Therapy) System (Avance® Pump and Avance® Foam Abdominal Dressing Kit) in Subjects With Open Abdominal Wounds</official_title>
