  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigation is a Post Marketing Follow-Up Study for the Avance Foam Abdominal Dressing
      Kit conducted as part of Mölnlycke Health Care's quality system. The primary objective is to
      evaluate the dressing kit as part of a negative pressure system. The secondary objectives are
      to collect and evaluate safety data, performance data and information on technical
      complications.
    </textblock>
